rComments: Najwa was super sweet! Her exams and quizzes are fair just make sure you review the material.. All in all she's amazing!!

Najwa was an amazing professor, she was very encouraging and helped each of us individually. I strongly recommend her classes. There were no large assignments, but routine practice was essential to success.

Prof Najwa was the sweetest prof and person I've ever had. You can tell she really cares about her students and their learning. She is very knowledgable in Arabic and is good at teaching it to beginners. You NEED the textbook, the class is based on it. She also takes attendance for the lectures and DGD, which is easy marks. Overall a great class!

Najwa is such a gem! Seriously, the best professor out there. She is so kind, always encouraging and really makes you want to do well in her class. Honestly, Arabic is NOT easy but this prof definitely helps. I wish she could teach every single one of my Arabic classes because I'm going to miss her next semester.

One of the most amazing professors I have ever had in my life. She is so passionate about Arabic. She's so sweet, and she really wants you to pass. I strongly recommend taking this course with her. She will make you fall in love with Arabic.
AMAZINGGGGG and honestly the nicest professor ever!!! she brings back hope to humanity :P and her testes/exam are very fair

THE BEST teacher of ottawaU! Elle a un don de mettre chaque élèque en confiance et de se sentire spéciale. Elle rend la matière simple et fun to learn. I miss her class! Take her, c'est de loin la meilleure prof d'arabe, je les ais tous passer et sans aucun doute la meilleure, la plus gentille et la plus passionnée.

Professor Najwa is an extremely kind, caring, and compassionate person. She tries to know all of her students' abilities and personalities, so that she can adapt to them and ease the learning process. ARB1911 is NOT and easy course, but Dr. Garzouzi makes it easy, fun, and interesting. I recommend her for all ARB courses.
Amazing prof!!! She is very patient and kind. She will make sure you do well if you're trying. Very helpful professor and definitely one of the sweetest I have ever had. Highly recommended!!
Amazing professor!! Very kind and always there to help. She will make sure you do well in her class if you're trying. Highly recommended

Awesome prof!!! Very patient and helpful. I took three classes with her and I would take more if I could. A lot of material to cover, and if she sees that you're not giving enough effort, it might affect your final mark. Overall, I recommend her classes to everyone.
She is adorable! As long as she knows you are making an effort, you will do very well. I loved this class. She is forgetful at times but overall she is a great prof!

Great proff. She really cares about her students and is always ready and willing to help. Her exams and midterms are always straightforward exactly like what she says in class. She is always smiling and patient with the students. The only down side is that she knows NOTHING about tech ( couldn't properly use the DVD that came with the book). Also this course does have a large workload and lots of memorizing but is extremely enjoyable if u like learning new languages
She's nice but the class is a LOT harder than portrayed here.

Najwa is a very kind person and a fantastic professor. The class is not easy (unless you already speak arabic), there is a large course load (homework, memorization, studying, assignments) but she makes it fun and interesting. She gets to know the level of every student and remains conscious of this throughout the course. Highly recommended.

yes she is very nice and a perfect teacher for beginner arabic, but i found these ratings to portray the class much easier than it is, it is demanding and challenging and a good memory is needed! its not as easy as it sounds BUT it is veryyy interesting and i've learned a lot! ps - if you know arabic don't take the class you cheaters :(

She is AWEsome...she is soo sweet, incredibly understandable, knows her stuff, lots of patience, loving, smiles all the time, love her accent and she will give u motherly love. Highly recommend to take her class

OMG! She is incredible & so nice! It was like kindergarten! Non-Arabic ppl, DO take it! Every1 came out with at least an A-. If u get less than an A-, then u were prolly vegetatin. To do Well: Astgs- do them all! It's just writing the alphabet (EASY!) Particptn- come 2 class and read one word. MTs & Final - she tells u the q's! U'll have a blast!
Of course she's a great prof she's lebanese!!! lol. She's very understanding and kind. Her tests are very straightforward (exactly as she outlines them).
Wicked prof!!!
Extremely approachable and friendly. Always available for consultation. Fair and easygoing attitude. Respects students.
Awesome professor who's not just fair but really easy going. Shes so helpful and nice.
she is such a nice prof! always smiling and willing to help out.  she understands us well and marks fairly ;).  i really like attending class because of the friendly atmosphere.
Such a nice prof - Assignments read: A+, A+, A+...
The best language teacher I have ever had...she is patient, organized, and has a lot of experience teaching.
